Malena Alterio https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malena_Alterio 0 Malena Grisel Alterio Bacaicoa (born 21 January 1974 in Buenos Aires, Argentina) is an Argentine-born Spanish actress. She became well-known with the Spanish TV series Aquí no hay quien viva, playing the role of Belén López Vázquez.
